react it is an opwn source cross platform js library which is use to develop user interface(Ui) (fornted end)

view layer (presentation layer)
it is maintained by facebook
with the help of it we can develop SPA
spa are those application which develop in only one page (index.html) , the content is update in a page withOUt refering

feature of js
component based architecture -componet are the core bulding block of react application 
they are used for reusability with  the help of it we can divide our code into small pieces of code
jsx javascript syntax extension where we can write html within javascript in rexat we have a babel transpile into jsx to js more read code
virtual Dom  virtual represtation of real dom due to this the perforamance of the application is fast

set up
nodejs 
npm create-react-app-appname
npm start

   -> Folder or directory structure
      -> node_modules : core modules for a react application
         -> public :- where we define our public files like assets and all
            -> index.html : it is a main file which execute when react
               application is running
               <div id="root"></div>
         -> src : it is a main folder of the application where we create all
            component , services and all
            App.js : default component
         index.html it is main entery file

hoew react application is boot or execute
index.html
<div id = "root"></div> ---> src/index.js --> it get the id root form index.html and load the app componet in the div id root.

 


